Package reck

Interface Summary
Corpus An interface that act as a corpus containing a list of documents.
Document An interface that act as a document containing a list of entities, relations and parse trees.
Entity An interface that act as an entity containing a list of mentions.
EntitySet An interface that act as a set of entities.
Mention An interface that act as an entity mention.
MentionList An interface that act as a list of mentions.
RECKParseTree An interface that act as a parse tree containing the constituent/ dependency parse trees
Relation An interface that act as a relation.
RelationSet An interface that act as a set of relations.
